This is a simple Ruby library for interacting directly with the database of Canvas LMS from Instructure.

Not ready for prime time. Patches welcome.

A MySQL connection:
DataMapper.setup(:heddle, Heddle::DatabaseConnectionString)

gem 'data_mapper'
gem 'dm-core'
gem 'dm-sqlite-adapter'
gem 'dm-timestamps'
gem 'dm-validations'
gem 'dm-aggregates'
gem 'dm-migrations'
gem 'dm-mysql-adapter'
gem 'activerecord-jdbc-adapter'
gem 'jdbc-mysql'
